text: Michaela Sejpalová (born 6 February 1998) is a Czech short track speed skater. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female short track speed skaters Category:Olympic short track speed skaters of the Czech Republic Category:Short track speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics
